title: Infographic: 26 Ideas For Split Testing Your Search Ads
excerpt: If you want to always be closing, then you need to always be testing, a long-standing mantra (and title of a popular book) in the search marketing space.

title: 11 A/B Testing Tools to Optimize Conversions
excerpt: A/B testing, the process of exposing randomized visitors to one or more variables, is among the most effective strategies to optimize user experiences and conversion rates. Here is a list of A/B testing tools.

title: 25 Ecommerce A/B Testing Ideas For Your 5 Top Store Pages
excerpt: The biggest question in ecommerce A/B testing is not “how.”

title: Comparing A/B and Multivariate Testing
excerpt: A/B tests are controlled experiments of two attributes, to measure which one was most popular with users. You can apply A/B testing to just about anything that you can measure. Multivariate testing allows you to measure multiple variables simultaneously.
